0 / min: Milestone Reached. Farming Plot Mk2, the seed extractor, Tree Plot and irrigation module have been unlocked. The Farming Plot mk2 is an upgrade to allow a liquid input to be used by the irrigation module for better crop efficiency. The Tree Plot can be used to farm trees. In addition the Seed extractor can be used to automate the production of seeds, with the added ability to output 2 seeds of the same crop that was inserted. Note. The seed extractor can also accept any input of a biomass product for the output of a randomized seed.
